Class MazeState_Impl

  • java.lang.Object
    • nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.a3.maze.MazeState_Impl

    MazeState

    public class MazeState_Impl
extends java.lang.Object
implements MazeState
    Implements the MazeState interface and describes the state of a maze (a level) including the board, items, chap, and enemies.
